WEBVTT

01:47.190 --> 01:50.819
That’s why, depending
on Tao compatibility,

01:50.902 --> 01:53.196
I’ll protect you strategically.

01:54.739 --> 01:56.449
We’re both ninja,

01:57.033 --> 01:59.160
but you and I are completely different.

01:59.828 --> 02:02.705
My life comes first for me.

02:03.289 --> 02:05.291
There's no way I'm risking my life!

02:05.375 --> 02:06.543
I’m the same.

02:07.669 --> 02:09.838
My goal is to return alive.

02:10.421 --> 02:12.841
To live... and see my wife.

02:13.424 --> 02:15.844
I have no intention of risking my life.

02:16.928 --> 02:18.847
That’s enough...

02:45.456 --> 02:47.125
All right, mission complete.

02:47.709 --> 02:48.877
Let’s withdraw.

02:49.669 --> 02:50.503
Make sure you don’t leave anything behind.

02:51.254 --> 02:52.505
Gabimaru.

02:53.089 --> 02:54.757
You’ve been acting strange lately.

02:54.841 --> 02:57.468
You’ve stopped killing on every mission.

03:00.722 --> 03:02.056
Back in the day,

03:02.140 --> 03:05.393
you’d have wiped out any obstacles
before starting the job.

03:05.977 --> 03:07.437
What's wrong with it?

03:07.520 --> 03:10.398
- The mission was just to take this.
- Could it be that...

03:10.481 --> 03:13.067
marriage changed your mindset?

03:16.154 --> 03:17.739
Just getting married...

03:17.822 --> 03:19.407
wouldn't change my heart.

03:22.076 --> 03:24.871
Oh, welcome back!

03:27.957 --> 03:29.167
Dear!

03:32.420 --> 03:34.881
You’re not injured today.

03:34.964 --> 03:36.883
I’m relieved.

03:36.966 --> 03:40.386
Lately... killing and stuff...

03:40.470 --> 03:42.889
I haven’t had any work like that.

03:42.972 --> 03:44.265
I see.

03:45.683 --> 03:47.018
I'm glad.

03:49.354 --> 03:50.605
I'm glad!

03:52.941 --> 03:54.525
It’s not a change of heart.

03:54.609 --> 03:56.236
I’m just confused.

03:56.736 --> 03:58.363
All my life,

03:58.446 --> 04:01.574
I’ve only lived as a ninja,

04:03.534 --> 04:05.745
but now I don’t even know
what face to make.

04:10.792 --> 04:13.461
It... It's my favorite!

04:14.087 --> 04:15.088
Chestnut rice!

04:17.298 --> 04:19.384
‎I see.

04:19.467 --> 04:21.719
I don’t even know what face to make.

04:22.428 --> 04:25.139
So, what’s today’s mission?

04:26.557 --> 04:28.476
Killing.

04:28.559 --> 04:31.396
Gabimaru, empty of blood and tears,

04:31.479 --> 04:34.315
that’s my true face.

04:37.318 --> 04:38.528
Welcome...

04:40.405 --> 04:41.739
Don't come closer.

04:42.323 --> 04:43.992
My face looks terrible.

04:44.575 --> 04:45.952
It will only scare you.

04:51.916 --> 04:52.875
S... Stop!

04:53.751 --> 04:55.837
You’ll get dirty...

05:01.009 --> 05:04.554
A... Aren’t you scared?

05:04.637 --> 05:06.514
Why would I be scared of you?

05:07.682 --> 05:10.101
You're not a demon or a spirit, after all.

05:10.184 --> 05:12.020
No matter what face you have,

05:12.729 --> 05:14.355
you’re my husband.

05:18.276 --> 05:19.360
As expected...

05:20.403 --> 05:23.364
I don't even know what face to make.

05:24.741 --> 05:27.368
But I don't want

05:28.161 --> 05:29.078
to cloud her face.

05:30.913 --> 05:31.789
Yui...

05:45.720 --> 05:48.973
My goal is to return alive,
to see my wife.

05:49.849 --> 05:52.185
I have no intention of risking my life.

05:54.062 --> 05:55.104
So...

05:57.732 --> 05:59.484
I’ll risk everything except my life.

06:04.697 --> 06:06.282
My beliefs...

06:07.200 --> 06:09.702
my logic, my common sense.

06:11.245 --> 06:12.830
Even my humanity.

06:45.279 --> 06:46.405
Gabimaru...

06:46.489 --> 06:48.908
I'm sure he used a second technique.

06:48.991 --> 06:51.410
A... secondary technique?

06:52.537 --> 06:54.413
When a person merges with a flower,

06:54.997 --> 06:58.000
if the flower’s Tao wins,
they turn into a flower.

06:58.084 --> 07:01.087
But if both balance each other,

07:01.170 --> 07:02.922
they gain the flower’s power.

07:03.506 --> 07:04.924
Same with Tensen.

07:07.593 --> 07:09.220
So then, my brother...

07:09.303 --> 07:10.138
Yes.

07:10.638 --> 07:12.932
But he won against the flower’s Tao.

07:13.015 --> 07:15.852
The elixir from the flower
entered his body,

07:15.935 --> 07:17.854
but the amount was small.

07:17.937 --> 07:21.357
So the Tao balanced out.

07:21.441 --> 07:24.861
He ended up with a body like a Tensen’s.

07:24.944 --> 07:27.363
So, if we can control
the flower transformation,

07:27.447 --> 07:30.783
we could gain the same
regenerative power as the Tensen.

07:31.451 --> 07:33.369
Then there’s something I want to test.

07:35.496 --> 07:36.873
Mu Dan's tendrils...

07:37.582 --> 07:39.750
Using this, one can
voluntarily flower-transform.

07:40.418 --> 07:42.295
The amount and balance
seem easier to adjust.

07:42.378 --> 07:43.212
Too dangerous!

07:44.213 --> 07:46.048
The balance was by chance.

07:46.132 --> 07:49.260
Normally, even a small amount
would trigger flower transformation.

07:49.343 --> 07:50.595
But Chobe did it.

07:53.848 --> 07:54.891
Why was that?

07:56.517 --> 07:59.896
Probably because he was near death.

08:01.564 --> 08:04.984
Tao is consumed

08:05.610 --> 08:07.653
by breathing, thinking, living.

08:08.821 --> 08:13.451
But on the edge of death,
you do nothing, you think nothing,

08:13.534 --> 08:18.289
so the Tao focused only on regeneration.

08:19.040 --> 08:19.916
I see.

08:19.999 --> 08:21.542
No, you do not!

08:21.626 --> 08:23.711
Chobe is special.

08:23.794 --> 08:26.797
Even unconscious, he can win
against the flower’s Tao.

08:26.881 --> 08:28.174
His self is strong.

08:28.257 --> 08:30.051
His will to live is strong.

08:30.134 --> 08:33.513
My brother is special. Just give up.

08:33.596 --> 08:35.681
You’re like everyone else.

08:35.765 --> 08:39.352
Even if you stab one, you'll just
turn into a flower, and that’s the end.

08:39.936 --> 08:41.604
Chobe was different from the others

08:42.188 --> 08:44.106
because he had something to lose.

08:47.068 --> 08:48.986
He was determined
because he had someone else

08:49.070 --> 08:51.697
and couldn't allow himself to die.

08:52.573 --> 08:54.283
No matter what else he lost.

08:55.326 --> 08:57.245
So he could survive,

08:57.328 --> 08:59.205
he abandoned being human.

09:00.414 --> 09:01.499
That’s...

09:01.582 --> 09:03.334
The secondary technique...

09:05.086 --> 09:06.837
It’s extreme...

09:08.839 --> 09:10.132
but...

09:10.216 --> 09:11.968
for Gabimaru, it's possible.

09:12.051 --> 09:14.387
No, I'm sure he'll do it.

09:14.971 --> 09:16.722
If it brings him even a little closer

09:17.223 --> 09:18.975
to his wife.

09:32.363 --> 09:33.698
Even with regenerative power,

09:33.781 --> 09:36.450
the battle won’t change much.

09:40.288 --> 09:41.956
The opponent has overcoming.

09:43.499 --> 09:45.835
Regeneration and Tao are weakened.

09:45.918 --> 09:48.588
Durability increases only slightly.

09:49.422 --> 09:53.509
You must avoid fatal wounds,
especially to the Tan Den,

09:53.593 --> 09:55.094
that goes for both of us.

09:55.177 --> 09:57.221
But that’s enough.

09:57.305 --> 09:59.348
That alone is sufficient.

10:00.349 --> 10:01.851
Sufficient to kill Ran

10:02.518 --> 10:04.729
before my body is consumed by the flower.

10:22.204 --> 10:23.914
You’re insane.

10:23.998 --> 10:27.918
Keep fighting, die once,

10:28.002 --> 10:29.920
abandon your humanity...

10:31.339 --> 10:33.758
All for something not even certain.

10:34.759 --> 10:38.304
It’s foolish. I can’t go along with it.

10:39.847 --> 10:41.599
That may be true.

10:43.100 --> 10:43.934
But...

10:45.144 --> 10:47.647
some places can only
be reached by foolishness.

10:48.397 --> 10:51.108
Calm or logic won’t get you there.

10:51.859 --> 10:54.570
Sometimes you can only rely on instinct.

10:55.404 --> 10:57.615
You’re selfish, but smart.

10:58.115 --> 10:59.325
You wouldn't understand

10:59.408 --> 11:02.119
what it is that can
make you act like a fool.

11:04.747 --> 11:05.790
Right?

11:05.873 --> 11:09.335
Smart people
don’t fight unwinnable battles.

11:14.840 --> 11:16.092
But...

11:17.218 --> 11:19.887
someone who tore your favorite clothes...

11:19.970 --> 11:21.138
is unforgivable.

11:21.722 --> 11:23.265
They're not yours.

11:26.227 --> 11:30.648
With my fire Tao, I can’t deal
a fatal blow to Ran’s water Tao.

11:31.357 --> 11:34.026
But with your earth Tao, you could do it.

11:34.110 --> 11:36.237
Even with overcoming Tao,

11:36.320 --> 11:38.531
if the difference is too great,
it becomes ineffective, right?

11:39.865 --> 11:44.203
And unlike Mu Dan, she keeps
her intelligence even after transforming.

11:44.286 --> 11:46.997
Will a makeshift
coordinated attack even work?

11:47.081 --> 11:48.916
That’s exactly why it will work.

11:50.584 --> 11:53.254
To be honest, it’s a gamble,

11:53.838 --> 11:55.005
but it can’t be helped.

11:55.923 --> 11:57.299
I'm doing this for my wife.

11:57.383 --> 11:59.510
Ah, yes, yes, that.

11:59.593 --> 12:02.888
Even after abandoning humanity, you’re
still the same, makes me oddly relieved.

12:04.974 --> 12:09.395
Ninjutsu... amazing training and refinement!

12:13.732 --> 12:15.359
Ninpo: Oni Hotaru!

12:17.862 --> 12:19.363
Ninja Art: Fire Bridge

12:24.535 --> 12:27.204
Ugh! I was going
to slam you to the ground.

12:27.288 --> 12:28.747
This still works!

12:35.713 --> 12:37.590
Ninja Art: Fire Monk

12:49.727 --> 12:51.604
That's hot! Move!

12:56.192 --> 12:58.986
Nothing will change,
no matter how many times you try.

12:59.695 --> 13:03.741
I know what your plan is.

13:03.824 --> 13:06.243
Your coordination is immature.

13:06.327 --> 13:09.622
It's a useless struggle, but...

13:10.206 --> 13:12.249
it's beautiful!

13:12.333 --> 13:15.794
A desperate battle... ninjutsu...

13:15.878 --> 13:21.133
The crystallized skill
of an imperfect human!

13:21.800 --> 13:23.052
That's not all.

13:23.928 --> 13:25.763
There's the ninjutsu
that can kill you too.

13:28.390 --> 13:31.769
Fine. Show me everything.

13:32.394 --> 13:34.730
All of it is training me.

13:34.813 --> 13:37.233
It's fuel for guiding Tao.

13:38.817 --> 13:41.487
Do we really need to provoke him?!

13:41.570 --> 13:42.738
It's fine.

13:42.821 --> 13:45.115
This is our only path to victory.

13:45.199 --> 13:47.243
Ah, geez!

13:47.326 --> 13:49.954
Fine, fine, let's do it!

14:35.708 --> 14:38.043
Tao is consumed

14:38.794 --> 14:41.297
by breathing, thinking, living.

14:41.881 --> 14:44.508
Then kishikai would also consume a lot.

14:45.301 --> 14:47.303
After the transformation ends,

14:47.386 --> 14:50.055
Tao is fully spent.

14:50.139 --> 14:52.433
They may end up with less than us.

14:52.516 --> 14:54.727
Is that so?

14:54.810 --> 14:55.686
Yes.

14:57.229 --> 14:59.857
Kishikai uses a lot of Tao.

14:59.940 --> 15:01.942
It won't last longer than half an hour.

15:03.152 --> 15:04.486
Half an hour...

15:04.570 --> 15:06.113
That’s long for a battle.

15:10.242 --> 15:12.119
Is it over already?

15:13.871 --> 15:16.498
Yeah, that'll do it.

15:19.001 --> 15:20.878
I know that external reactions

15:21.462 --> 15:23.756
are the same as a human’s.

15:23.839 --> 15:25.507
Even to light.

15:27.843 --> 15:30.012
So with excessive flashing,

15:30.095 --> 15:32.640
we can create a temporary state
of nerve excitation.

15:35.517 --> 15:37.686
Over-concentration from excitement

15:37.770 --> 15:40.731
takes away judgment and sense of time.

15:41.231 --> 15:44.526
A standard technique
during ninja interrogation.

15:45.527 --> 15:46.820
There's no way...

15:46.904 --> 15:49.949
We were buying time, waiting for this.

15:51.450 --> 15:53.243
That’s long for a battle.

15:53.327 --> 15:55.496
But if you endure half an hour...

15:56.455 --> 15:57.623
It's a rare chance.

15:58.832 --> 16:00.376
Kishikai collapses.

16:01.794 --> 16:03.796
After Kishikai is undone,

16:03.879 --> 16:05.422
their power disappears.

16:06.382 --> 16:09.551
They are untouchable, god-like beings.

16:10.636 --> 16:14.306
So we pull them into our range.

16:16.433 --> 16:17.643
It's our only chance

16:18.519 --> 16:20.145
to target their original Tao!

16:27.861 --> 16:29.446
Before he used up all his Tao,

16:29.530 --> 16:31.824
he released the transformation himself!

16:33.909 --> 16:36.912
He's circulating Yin and Yang
and recovering Tao!

16:36.996 --> 16:41.083
Yuzuriha! Destroy Ran's Tan Den with
your overcoming Tao before he recovers!

16:41.166 --> 16:43.335
She can't do that.

16:44.586 --> 16:45.838
I can see it.

16:46.422 --> 16:48.173
Her serious injuries.

16:48.257 --> 16:50.092
She's barely standing.

16:50.175 --> 16:53.846
If she gathers Tao into
her weapons, she’ll die.

16:54.972 --> 16:58.726
She’s not willing to risk her life.

16:59.476 --> 17:00.978
That's right.

17:01.061 --> 17:03.647
I come first.

17:04.940 --> 17:07.693
I'll just end up dead if I do it.

17:08.193 --> 17:09.194
But...

17:10.612 --> 17:12.781
letting you live

17:12.865 --> 17:15.826
will stress me to death anyway, I think.

17:16.910 --> 17:20.372
In the end, you’ve got
to do what you want.

17:20.873 --> 17:24.001
Life isn’t just about breathing.

17:26.378 --> 17:27.379
Fine.

17:29.673 --> 17:31.258
That's enough now.

17:40.934 --> 17:44.021
You’ve got to do what you want.

17:59.578 --> 18:01.538
Life isn't just about breathing.

18:29.024 --> 18:32.653
My poor... brother...

18:38.200 --> 18:39.409
You okay?

18:39.493 --> 18:40.786
Hey, are you?

18:40.869 --> 18:43.038
I only got pierced through by a pillar.

18:43.831 --> 18:45.207
The overcoming Tao has no effect.

18:45.916 --> 18:48.127
It’ll take time, but I'll regenerate.

18:48.627 --> 18:51.296
But it’s not perfect, right?

18:52.005 --> 18:56.051
The more you regenerate,
the more your body turns to tree.

18:56.135 --> 18:58.303
Like the wooden people.

18:59.346 --> 19:01.765
Limited regenerative power.

19:01.849 --> 19:03.851
You die if you get harmed too much.

19:03.934 --> 19:06.061
An even worse hell may await.

19:06.770 --> 19:08.814
Still, to return to my wife,

19:09.398 --> 19:10.941
there was no other way.

19:11.024 --> 19:13.152
Truly admirable.

19:13.235 --> 19:15.154
All right, if you’re okay, let’s go.

19:15.237 --> 19:18.490
No way! You're joking, right?!
Let me rest!

19:19.324 --> 19:20.450
There's no time.

19:21.451 --> 19:22.953
We have to chase down Sagiri and Mei.

19:23.036 --> 19:27.624
Also, currently, it’s unclear
who will reach the water gate.

19:27.708 --> 19:30.002
We may need to get ahead.

19:30.878 --> 19:32.296
Then go ahead first.

19:32.796 --> 19:34.923
I’ll catch up after resting.

19:35.716 --> 19:37.551
Are you really okay?

19:37.634 --> 19:39.887
Oh, you’re worried about me?

19:39.970 --> 19:42.639
Surprising! If your wife
found out, she’d be mad.

19:42.723 --> 19:45.100
She’s not that petty.

19:46.393 --> 19:49.438
I’m fine, really. Go ahead!

19:50.230 --> 19:51.607
I'll be waiting for you.

19:55.652 --> 19:56.612
Yuzuriha...

19:56.695 --> 19:58.614
Huh? There's more?

19:58.697 --> 20:00.115
Thank you for saving me.

20:01.658 --> 20:02.951
I mean that sincerely.

20:11.460 --> 20:14.713
Ugh, he really got me.

20:14.796 --> 20:17.257
It's pretty deep.

20:18.800 --> 20:22.137
I guess I got a little carried away.
It’s not like me.

20:23.388 --> 20:25.182
Rin, Pyo, To, Sha,

20:25.265 --> 20:27.684
Kai, Jin, Retsu, Zai, Zen...

20:27.768 --> 20:31.480
I never show anyone anything sincere.

20:31.980 --> 20:34.107
Living, dying...

20:35.150 --> 20:37.152
I'll do it alone.

20:37.236 --> 20:40.155
Do I need a reason
for just wanting to come back alive?

20:40.239 --> 20:44.660
I don't want to die this young, that's it!

20:46.912 --> 20:49.289
I'm sorry, Saya.

20:50.457 --> 20:55.420
Your big sister tried to live as fully
as she could, for your sake too.

20:57.381 --> 21:00.092
Guess this is it.

21:00.175 --> 21:04.346
When it gets tough,
just think about the things you like.

21:06.056 --> 21:08.392
Like cats, or people you love.

21:09.226 --> 21:13.522
Your family...
Just picture beautiful scenery.

21:29.121 --> 21:30.247
This is unexpected.

21:30.747 --> 21:31.790
No...

21:31.873 --> 21:35.002
It’s only natural
that imperfect Tao would prevail.

21:36.503 --> 21:37.754
Where are you going?

21:38.463 --> 21:39.923
To report to Rien.

21:40.507 --> 21:42.801
You can do as you please.

21:43.302 --> 21:44.970
Is that okay?

21:45.721 --> 21:47.514
You're just going to leave us here?

21:47.597 --> 21:48.849
It doesn't matter.

21:48.932 --> 21:50.976
I told you,
I have no intention of fighting.

21:51.059 --> 21:53.812
You... You're not going
to avenge your comrades?

21:53.895 --> 21:54.938
Nope.

21:55.022 --> 21:58.942
If they get eliminated, then that’s
just part of the training process.

21:59.026 --> 22:02.696
Even Mei, the leader,
should have understood that.

22:03.530 --> 22:06.158
Each Tensen is a seeker of the Way.

22:06.241 --> 22:08.243
There’s no bond, no affection.

22:08.327 --> 22:10.120
You were probably just
imitating what you saw, Mei.

22:10.871 --> 22:12.914
Ever since leaving Horai,

22:12.998 --> 22:15.751
you've just been hiding
and watching the island's decline.

22:16.335 --> 22:18.712
Why did you come back now?

22:21.214 --> 22:22.299
Life...

22:22.883 --> 22:24.384
I finally understand it.

22:24.468 --> 22:25.969
I was taught.

22:29.139 --> 22:30.223
I see.

22:30.724 --> 22:31.892
Must be nice.

22:35.312 --> 22:36.646
What was that noise?

22:44.905 --> 22:46.073
This doesn't look good.

24:23.962 --> 24:25.881
Subtitle translation by: Maslin Friedman
